{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-press-release-tsx","path":"/ar/media-center/sustainability-showcase-at-qatar-foundation-spotlights-partnerships","result":{"data":{"contentfulPagePressRelease":{"id":"27654189-61e9-5dd4-b3ed-fb20dc9b4065","slug":"sustainability-showcase-at-qatar-foundation-spotlights-partnerships","title":"مؤسسة قطر تسلط الضوء على شراكاتها، إنجازاتها، وريادتها في مجال الاستدامة","date":"2019-02-25","filterTags":null,"filterEntity":[{"contentful_id":"6osgodAE6cIuiqSAOQugAs"}],"heroImage":null,"modulesWrapper":[{"modules":[{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"3bba867a-a0cb-5997-8757-784e363cf838","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>تزامنًا مع الاحتفال بيوم البيئة القطري لعام 2019، وفي ظل الدور القيادي الذي تؤديه مؤسسة قطر فيما يتعلق بالتنمية المستدامة، وحرصها على توحيد الجهود الوطنية، وتعزيز أثر مبادراتها التي أطلقتها بالتعاون مع شركائها في هذا المجال داخل دولة قطر.</p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"53380162-c922-549e-8cee-a5d0d14e0f3c","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"e9789487-4264-559f-9e45-e30c1c0746c1","title":"QF Sustainability Event - Image 1","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":1450,"height":1008}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7id4cRf6ePmvg4zou8PDCv/69305a7a20e96be6a7a3b85ef0c47305/QF_Sustainability_Event_-__Image_1.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7id4cRf6ePmvg4zou8PDCv/69305a7a20e96be6a7a3b85ef0c47305/QF_Sustainability_Event_-__Image_1.jpg?w=280&h=150&q=85 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7id4cRf6ePmvg4zou8PDCv/69305a7a20e96be6a7a3b85ef0c47305/QF_Sustainability_Event_-__Image_1.jpg?w=560&h=300&q=85 560w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7id4cRf6ePmvg4zou8PDCv/69305a7a20e96be6a7a3b85ef0c47305/QF_Sustainability_Event_-__Image_1.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85 1120w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7id4cRf6ePmvg4zou8PDCv/69305a7a20e96be6a7a3b85ef0c47305/QF_Sustainability_Event_